  "format": "logseq",
  "sections": [
    {
      "heading": "扩大模数",
      "level": 2,
      "blocks": [
        {
          "heading": "求不了逆元",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>条件</strong>：$X$ 一定能被 $D$ 整除，要求 $(X / D) \\bmod M$。但 $\\gcd(D, M) > 1$，求不出逆元。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>操作</strong>：计算 $Y = X \\bmod (M \\times D)$，答案是 $(Y / D) \\bmod M$。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>证明</strong>：",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "因为是对 $M \\times D$ 取模，所以真实值 $X$ 可以写成：",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "math",
              "latex": "$$X = k \\cdot (M \\times D) + Y$$\n我们在等式两边同时除以 $D$。因为题目保证了 $X$ 能被 $D$ 整除，且 $k \\cdot (M \\times D)$ 显然也能被 $D$ 整除，所以 $Y$ 绝对能被 $D$ 完美整除。\n$$\\frac{X}{D} = k \\cdot M + \\frac{Y}{D}$$",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "我们要求的是最终答案对 $M$ 取模，等式两边同时对 $M$ 取模：",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "math",
              "latex": "$$\\frac{X}{D} \\bmod M = (k \\cdot M + \\frac{Y}{D}) \\bmod M$$\n因为 $k \\cdot M$ 是 $M$ 的倍数，取模直接消掉：\n$$\\frac{X}{D} \\bmod M = \\frac{Y}{D} \\bmod M$$",
              "depth": 2
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "heading": "下取整取模",
          "level": 3,
          "blocks": [
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>条件</strong>：$X$ 不一定能被 $D$ 整除，要求 $\\lfloor X / D \\rfloor \\bmod M$。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>操作</strong>：计算 $Y = X \\bmod (M \\times D)$，答案是 $\\lfloor Y / D \\rfloor \\bmod M$。",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "<strong>证明</strong>：",
              "depth": 1
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "同样，把真实值 $X$ 写出来：",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "math",
              "latex": "$$X = k \\cdot (M \\times D) + Y$$\n两边同时除以 $D$：\n$$\\frac{X}{D} = k \\cdot M + \\frac{Y}{D}$$",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "两边同时套上<strong>向下取整</strong>的符号 $\\lfloor \\dots \\rfloor$。",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "math",
              "latex": "$$\\lfloor \\frac{X}{D} \\rfloor = k \\cdot M + \\lfloor \\frac{Y}{D} \\rfloor$$\n两边同时对 $M$ 取模：\n$$\\lfloor \\frac{X}{D} \\rfloor \\bmod M = (k \\cdot M + \\lfloor \\frac{Y}{D} \\rfloor) \\bmod M$$",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "p",
              "html": "$k \\cdot M$ 被模掉，化简得到：",
              "depth": 2
            },
            {
              "type": "math",
              "latex": "$$\\lfloor \\frac{X}{D} \\rfloor \\bmod M = \\lfloor \\frac{Y}{D} \\rfloor \\bmod M$$",
              "depth": 2
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
